From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alexander Schiffhauer <alexander.schiffhauer@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 19 May 2026 10:25:38 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] winewayland.drv: Bridge DXVK back buffers to wl_subsurface via wl_shm.

Companion to the dcomp.dll implementation.  When dcomp delivers a
WM_WAYLAND_COMPOSE_ATTACH for a window, the wayland driver
needs to present that DXVK back buffer as a layer above (or in
place of) its existing CPU bitmap.  Add a Vulkan-to-wl_shm copy
path: a per-target host-visible VkBuffer receives
vkCmdCopyImageToBuffer output, the buffer is memcpy'd into a
wl_shm pool, and a wl_subsurface of the toplevel ancestor is
attached so the compositor composites CEF output on top of the
existing surface.

Additional small Wayland integrations bundled here because they
share the same surface plumbing:

  * wl_compositor_create_region empty input region for
    WS_EX_TRANSPARENT click-through (so the CEF subsurface does
    not intercept clicks intended for the wine toplevel).
  * wp_viewporter + wp_fractional_scale_v1 for crisp HiDPI
    (subsurface buffer is full device-pixel resolution, viewport
    maps it to logical surface coordinates).
  * wp_cursor_shape_v1 SHAPE_DEFAULT fallback so we don't need
    wl_cursor when the compositor advertises the protocol.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Schiffhauer <alexander.schiffhauer@gmail.com>
---
 dlls/winewayland.drv/Makefile.in         |    1 +
 dlls/winewayland.drv/waylanddrv.h        |   57 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 dlls/winewayland.drv/wayland_pointer.c   |   25 ++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 dlls/winewayland.drv/wayland_compose.c   |  427 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 dlls/winewayland.drv/wayland_surface.c   |  140 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 dlls/winewayland.drv/window.c            |   21 +++++++++++++++++----
 6 files changed, 666 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 dlls/winewayland.drv/wayland_compose.c

diff --git a/dlls/winewayland.drv/Makefile.in b/dlls/winewayland.drv/Makefile.in
index ea74828..5fa3ec9 100644
--- a/dlls/winewayland.drv/Makefile.in
+++ b/dlls/winewayland.drv/Makefile.in
@@ -26,6 +26,7 @@ SOURCES = \
 	wayland_keyboard.c \
